---
---

<header class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1 class="display reveal">
      A quiet place<br />
      to keep your<br />
      <em>little corners</em> of the web.
    </h1>
    <p class="lede reveal">
      Porvi is where you and a handful of friends write, ship, and tend to personal static
      sites - each with its own custom domain, its own voice, and zero ceremony between a commit
      and the world seeing it.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta reveal">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#cta">
        Request an invite
        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none">
          <path
            d="M2.5 6h7M6 2.5 9.5 6 6 9.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.4"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#how">
        Read the docs <span class="kbd">↵</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-meta reveal">
      <div class="meta-cell">
        <div class="num">Astro</div>
        <div class="label">Native framework</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-cell">
        <div class="num">/your.domain</div>
        <div class="label">Bring any domain</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-cell">
        <div class="num">~12s</div>
        <div class="label">Commit to live</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-cell">
        <div class="num">0 ¢</div>
        <div class="label">For friends</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
